doc: New wall objects placed in 8de2965 contains "banner text" info
Placing any size of wall objects in 8de2965 shows banner text info when the object placed is not a banner.
The info for another wall object on the same tile placed before 8de2965 properly shows "not a banner"
2. Tile Inspector info shows "banner text" where there should not be any
Affected save can be provided via private message because the park is being built for an ongoing competition
